Description:
   Recurrence Loop is a Psionicist offensive area spell. The caster
   establishes a recursive psionic feedback pattern that bounces between
   all enemies in the room, dealing psychic damage to each target it hits
   before looping back and repeating. The loop strikes multiple times,
   accumulating damage with each recurrence.

   The recurrence effect makes this spell valuable in fights with multiple
   opponents, as the looping damage can strike each enemy several times in
   a single casting. The number of loops and the intensity of each pass
   scales with the Psionicist's level and psionic power. The loop eventually
   dissipates when the feedback energy is fully expended, but a well-timed
   Recurrence Loop can deal enormous total damage spread across an entire
   enemy group.
